{"tid":1461032,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"去機場嘅小小建議","createTime":"2019-08-13T05:54:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T06:15:40.000Z","uid":279872,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1be4e925f6429b85dabaa0bb9de3b09bc235a7b4","tid":1461032,"uid":279872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:54:33.000Z","msg":"我係p牌但請睇左先鬧<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">現場篇</span></span><br />\n <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 英文口號</span></strong><br />\n去機場除左係要癱瘓，亦係要話比全世界知我地爭取嘅嘢同黑警嘅暴行。如果淨係叫廣東話，其實好多遊客根本唔會知咩事，甚至覺得困擾。所以不如下英文甚至其他外語嘅口號。尤其係接機大堂嘅，可以叫多D shame on Hong Kong police, free Hong Kong, Fight for democracy等等口號。琴日所見唔少外國人聽到都主動埋來睇下咩事。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2. 情報站</span></strong><br />\n琴日大家都見到對家點同我地打情報戰。係太多人，完全上唔到網睇消息嘅情況下真係好容易引發恐慌。小弟唔熟手機信號嘅原理，不過如果係中間或者機場兩側留返一兩個疏D嘅位用來做情報收集同FC唔知可唔可行？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>3. 同遊客道歉啊！</strong></span><br />\n比著你，搭左時幾個鐘飛機一落地就比十幾萬人圍著行都行唔到，你都可能燥啦。記住，好多遊客唔知黑警做過咩架。有機會嘅話友善D道個歉，順便同佢講吓發生咩事，叫佢見到警察小心D唔好咩<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">散水篇</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>1.往博覽館方向上機鐵</strong></span><br />\n一人多就一定有人係呢邊上機鐵，然後市區方向嘅就會上唔到。既然係咁，倒不如全部人係博覽館方向上車，留返下層比去搭巴士/行路/去T2嘅人。避免好似琴日咁塞住哂嘅局面<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2.企上凳</span></strong><br />\n琴日搭機鐵有份企嘅就會知。兩個位最多坐3嘅人。企嘅話逼少少企到5個，空出來嘅腳位又企到3-4個。呢D位有幾好用相信大家都知<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">3.搭機鐵嘅唔該去九龍/香港</span></strong><br />\n琴日行到出埃及記咁，你唔係仲去青衣同佢地爭位啊。搭機鐵嘅搭遠D落啦<br />\n<br />\nsorry for 1999"},{"pid":"c90abddae2e08eda4aa835ccce6e6cdb045d266e","tid":1461032,"uid":279872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:55:55.000Z","msg":"機場太大，小弟琴日都行唔哂。大家仲諗到咩嘅就一齊討論下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aab778eea87f0e57f02f5cefce4a718deb2ebdf","tid":1461032,"uid":279872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:56:10.000Z","msg":"自推5下"},{"pid":"a9a0e829dc4ac5e636deb957be72e04f538f9d9e","tid":1461032,"uid":279872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:56:28.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"e19ebba85f41e28836f1117e8444ecfb5ba93554","tid":1461032,"uid":295218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:56:42.000Z","msg":"你班連登傻仔，入乜撚嘢機場？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1460800\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1460800</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"809e2f1c70ac1e9488139b7ccc286c07e7fd35cb","tid":1461032,"uid":279872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:56:44.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"2713ec68e4f2e2d929f1a491b05978f3aa1cc1d1","tid":1461032,"uid":279872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:57:06.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"cb426ba89569132a77031c6e33c2d4268ccf259c","tid":1461032,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:57:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\">係林鄭將香港推向一個萬劫不復的深淵<br />\n係林鄭月娥忍心將香港推進粉身碎骨深淵</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"5f38f2ebb876ea5f4a1a78329c0e4e43de51c405","tid":1461032,"uid":279872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:57:24.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"59ac402cf271e9a8887fb1d82051a28c166792a5","tid":1461032,"uid":257736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:59:03.000Z","msg":"機場 見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80bb9b54db1de49c24e922a015687b4465086ce2","tid":1461032,"uid":202262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:01:04.000Z","msg":"Good article Must Push! 721 811"},{"pid":"deecafb2011e106010c1f29b43af616d0b788211","tid":1461032,"uid":76952,"like":0,"